sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 Usuario (WhatsApp)
    participant N8N as n8n
    participant NestJS as NestJS Webhook
    participant Queue as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant Orch as Orquestador LangGraph
    participant Agent as Agente (ej. Sales)
    participant Gemini as Gemini API
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Sup as Supervisor (Paperclip)

    User->>N8N: Mensaje WhatsApp
    N8N->>NestJS: POST /messaging/webhook\n[X-N8N-Secret]
    NestJS->>NestJS: N8nAuthGuard valida header
    NestJS->>PG: Crea/recupera Conversation\ngenera threadId (UUID v4)
    NestJS->>Queue: Encola job { threadId, message }
    NestJS-->>N8N: 202 Accepted

    Queue->>Orch: Dequeue (concurrency: 1)
    Orch->>Gemini: classify_intent(message)
    Gemini-->>Orch: AgentType = SALES

    Orch->>Agent: route_to_agent → SalesGraph
    Agent->>Chroma: retrieve_context(query, "ventas", topK=4)
    Chroma-->>Agent: [{doc, score}, ...]

    alt score máximo ≥ 0.7
        Agent->>Gemini: generate_response(context + message)
        Gemini-->>Agent: respuesta
        Agent->>PG: log OrchestrationEvent (ROUTED_TO_AGENT)
        Agent->>PG: log TokenUsage + durationMs
        Agent-->>Orch: respuesta final
        Orch->>N8N: POST /send-whatsapp { to, text }
        N8N->>User: Respuesta WhatsApp
    else score < 0.7 → escalate_to_human
        Agent->>Agent: interrupt() → checkpoint en PG
        Agent->>PG: status = WAITING_HUMAN
        Agent->>PG: log OrchestrationEvent (ESCALATED_TO_HUMAN)
        Note over Queue,Agent: Job completa exitosamente (no queda colgado)
        Sup->>NestJS: GET /admin/events (polling Paperclip)
        NestJS-->>Sup: eventos pendientes
        Sup->>NestJS: POST /admin/conversations/:threadId/resume\n{ supervisorMessage }
        NestJS->>Queue: Nuevo job { threadId, supervisorMessage }
        Queue->>Orch: Retoma desde checkpoint
        Orch->>N8N: Respuesta del supervisor
        N8N->>User: Respuesta WhatsApp
    end